{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/blog/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/blog/[slug]/layout,_N_T_/[locale]/blog/[slug]/page,_N_T_/ko/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--9I252HdFb11XW5eU1Wvtz--><html lang=\"ko\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"image\" href=\"/blog/optimize-images-hero.jpg\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/41ea5997d0ea9f4c.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-5f7aa716bc7d8d39.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-ebd51be49873d76c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-9fa8c0a1addc7277.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/707-a8cb8823e74114e8.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/blog/%5Bslug%5D/page-7182770d1703571a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/page-d5b8dc0a4bde352c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/%5Blocale%5D/layout-8ce825e7014413b5.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#7c3aed\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"\"/><title>웹사이트 속도와 SEO를 위한 이미지 최적화 방법 | ToolPic 블로그</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"더 빠른 웹사이트 로딩을 위한 이미지 최적화 방법을 알아보세요. 포맷 선택, 압축 기술, 지연 로딩, 반응형 이미지로 SEO를 개선합니다.\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/ko/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"en\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/en/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"zh\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/zh/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"ja\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/ja/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"ko\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/ko/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"es\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/es/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"fr\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/fr/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"de\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/de/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"pt\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/pt/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"ru\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/ru/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"ar\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/ar/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"hi\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/hi/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"it\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/it/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"tr\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/tr/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"vi\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/vi/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"th\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/th/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"id\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/id/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" hrefLang=\"nl\" href=\"https://toolpic.me/nl/blog/how-to-optimize-images-for-website-speed\"/><link rel=\"a